title: About Me
text:
Supply chain professional based out of the SF bay area. This is a personal blog, and views expressed here are my own.
Reach out to me for suggestions on what I can do on this blog! Social media links below.

title: Welcome To Muscle Memory Data Science!
text:
This blog is where I document everything - simple or complex, dull or interesting - as I work on practicing and developing my skills.
I hope this is useful for others and not just for me. Feel free to share your thoughts and suggestions in the comments section of the posts! The about page has my contact details if you wish to reach out to me.
